channel.title: Slayer Points problem
channel.description: When I try to add another item to my slayer points shop it won't allow me too, BUT when I switch and item with another item it allows me too. I'm guessing there is a maximum of 4 items allowed in the shop (thats how many I have in there). Is there a way to higher the maximum amount of items allowed in my slayer points shop?
